name: THE ANIMAL
description:
The Animal
Digital Noise Frontier and Domenico Barra audio/visual collaboration. 
Glitch meets databending.
This is the ecstasy of creation. visceral, primordial, animal instinct. 
The soundtrack to art revolta. Voice of sovereign artists, taking back control like never before!
This is The Animal on the Blockchain.
One of the pieces remixed here was the artwork made for the Remembrance track by Suicideyears part of Major Tendons curated by Molly Soda for New Hive, 2014.
